reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wise decision of buying this SSD
reviews.reviewText: I was so hesitant to buy this unknown brand of SSD; but I took a dare decision of going for it. The best part of this SSD is that comes with a screw which is necessary for install it. It was very easy to install; actually my 15 years old son installed it with no time.I have installed this SSD just 10 days ago; amazingly it work great and perfect. This is really worth for money.Lesson learnt: It is not necessary that the unknown brads should be low in quality and performance than the known brands. I'm so happy that I have decided to buy this and feel its a wide decision. Time has to tell how well it would work.I would recommend to buy this SSD with confidence.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 5500 speed best for gaming
reviews.reviewText: I bought this cheap 4Tb memory for the ps5. After I installed it, i realized that it is 5000 mb/s when the ps5 recommends minimum of 5500 mb/s. Well, it works just fine on the games I have tried. Rumor is that Ratchet and Clank needs full speed. I will keep that one on the main board. I think most everything else can go onto this.One thing. When assembling there are no instructions. Put the thick white pad on top of the square chips, and the thing grey pad on the flat bottom. Then align the two metal halves together on one side, and snap the other side together. I tried sliding it on, and no way that would ever work because of the exposed adhesive, hah. Works perfectly as best I can tell in ps5. If I had to do it over again, would have gotten the faster speed, but I guess I saved a few bucks and it hasnt seemed to matter.
